---
title: Sri Lankan-Spiced Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Mayonnaise & Flaked Almonds
description: Bring out the aromatic scents of a North Indian inspired spice mix and a warm palette of crispy roast veggies.
Combine them together to enrich your dinner with colour and flavour. You won’t be disappointed in how everything
tastes so undeniably good.

